===========================================
CHAT APP - DEVELOPMENT ROADMAP
===========================================
Last Updated: 26 October 2025

===========================================
PRIORITY 1: REAL-TIME CHAT LIST UPDATES
===========================================
Issue: When user B sends a message to user A for the first time, 
       the new chat doesn't appear in A's chat list without refreshing the page.

Tasks:
  [ ] Backend - Emit socket event when new chat is created
      - Update message.controllers.js to emit 'new-chat-created' event
      - Include chat details and participants info
  
  [ ] Frontend - Listen for new chat socket events
      - Add socket listener in SocketContext.tsx or chat component
      - Update chat list state when new chat is received
  
  [ ] Frontend - Update chat list UI dynamically
      - Add new chat to the top of the chat list
      - Handle duplicate prevention
      - Show notification/indicator for new chat
  
  [ ] Testing
      - Test with two users who haven't chatted before
      - Verify chat appears immediately without refresh
      - Test with multiple concurrent new chats

