PRIORITY 2: GROUP CHAT FUNCTIONALITY
===========================================
Tasks:
  [ ] Backend - Group Chat Creation
      - Create API endpoint for creating group chats
      - Support multiple participants (3+ users)
      - Add group name and group avatar fields
      - Update chat.controllers.js
  
  [ ] Backend - Add/Remove Members
      - API to add new members to existing group
      - API to remove members from group
      - Handle permission checks (admin/creator only)
      - Emit socket events for member changes
  
  [ ] Frontend - Group Chat UI
      - Create group chat creation dialog/modal
      - Multi-select user picker component
      - Display group name and avatar
      - Show group member list
  
  [ ] Frontend - Group Chat Features
      - Add member interface
      - Remove member interface
      - Leave group functionality
      - Admin controls
  
  [ ] Database Updates
      - Update Chats model to support group type
      - Add group metadata (name, avatar, admin)
      - Update chat-member associations
  
  [ ] Socket Events
      - new-group-created
      - member-added
      - member-removed
      - group-updated

