PRIORITY 5: VIDEO & AUDIO CALLS
===========================================
This will be implemented last

Tasks:
  [ ] Technology Selection
      - Choose WebRTC library (e.g., simple-peer, PeerJS)
      - Or use service like Agora, Twilio
  
  [ ] Backend - Signaling Server
      - WebRTC signaling via Socket.io
      - Handle call initiation
      - Handle call acceptance/rejection
      - Handle call end/disconnect
      - Room management for group calls
  
  [ ] Frontend - Call UI Components
      - Call initiation buttons (video/audio)
      - Incoming call notification/modal
      - Call screen with video/audio controls
      - Screen sharing option
      - Mute/unmute controls
      - Camera on/off toggle
      - End call button
  
  [ ] One-to-One Calls
      - Voice call functionality
      - Video call functionality
      - Call quality indicators
      - Reconnection handling
  
  [ ] Group Calls (Optional)
      - Support multiple participants
      - Grid/spotlight view
      - Participant management
  
  [ ] Socket Events
      - call-initiated
      - call-accepted
      - call-rejected
      - call-ended
      - ice-candidate
      - offer/answer exchange

