===========================================
NOTES & CONSIDERATIONS
===========================================
- Ensure all socket events are properly handled on both client and server
- Maintain backward compatibility during database migrations
- Consider scalability for file storage (use cloud storage for production)
- Implement proper authentication and authorization for all new features
- Keep UI consistent with existing design system
- Test all features across different screen sizes
- Consider accessibility (a11y) in UI components

